The NHL cancels all games through 14 December, plus the 2013 NHL All-Star Game scheduled for 27 January in Columbus, Ohio, due to the 2012 NHL lockout. (The Guardian)Jamaican sprinter Usain Bolt and British athlete Jessica Ennis are awarded the 2013 Laureus World Sports Awards. (Laureus) (BBC)Juventus stays six points clear at the top of the 2012–13 Serie A after earning a 1–1 draw at second-place Napoli. (CNN) (Goal.com)